      "text": "8歌&卷毛",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 5.63,
      "time_str": "00:05.630",
      "text": "歌词制作：8歌",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 7.31,
      "time_str": "00:07.310",
      "text": "人声录音：小风是我@Jcv Studio",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 8.92,
      "time_str": "00:08.920",
      "text": "母带：小风是我@Jcv Studio/卷毛",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 10.47,
      "time_str": "00:10.470",
      "text": "混音工作室：CurlyColor Studio",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 11.27,
      "time_str": "00:11.270",
      "text": "母带工作室：CurlyColor Studio",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 14.5,
      "time_str": "00:14.500",
      "text": "毛：从并肩而行到追逐背影",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 17.79,
      "time_str": "00:17.790",
      "text": "将疏远诠释得很彻底",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 21.75,
      "time_str": "00:21.750",
      "text": "8：这仓促剧情没挽留余地",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 25.04,
      "time_str": "00:25.040",
      "text": "脱离被爱轨迹",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 28.51,
      "time_str": "00:28.510",
      "text": "毛：世界另一边的",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 30.43,
      "time_str": "00:30.430",
      "text": "8：你曾惬意的靠近只是事到如今",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 34.04,
      "time_str": "00:34.040",
      "text": "毛：已被注定平行",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 36.02,
      "time_str": "00:36.020",
      "text": "8：可早已经约定炙热的双手握紧",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 39.49,
      "time_str": "00:39.490",
      "text": "毛：誓言太过违心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 42.85,
      "time_str": "00:42.850",
      "text": "8：倘若你与我终究陌路在旅程尽头",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 46.44,
      "time_str": "00:46.440",
      "text": "我何必在开篇启程时过分期待以后",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.1,
      "time_str": "00:50.100",
      "text": "相遇的最后竟然只能够擦肩而过",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 53.75,
      "time_str": "00:53.750",
      "text": "怪我没预判到结果",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.29,
      "time_str": "00:57.290",
      "text": "倘若你与我终究陌路在旅程尽头",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 60.88,
      "time_str": "01:00.880",
      "text": "在沿途欣赏风景时就不该留念太久",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.53,
      "time_str": "01:04.530",
      "text": "贪心的想将你温柔全部都占为己有",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 68.19,
      "time_str": "01:08.190",
      "text": "未曾想自始至终都 不是我",
      "translation": null
